---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Impressum & Privacy Policy — Yanis Amani"
  description="Legal notice and privacy policy (GDPR compliance) for Yanis Amani's portfolio."
>
  <section class="py-32 md:py-40">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 md:px-12">
      <div data-animate>
        <span class="section-num mb-6">§ Legal</span>
        <h1 class="display-md text-white mb-12">
          Impressum &<br/>
          <span class="text-[hsl(0,0%,35%)]">Privacy Policy</span>
        </h1>
      </div>

      <div class="space-y-12 text-[hsl(0,0%,70%)] text-sm leading-relaxed" data-animate data-delay="1">
        
        <!-- Impressum -->
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-4">1. Impressum (Legal Notice)</h2>
          <p class="mb-2"><strong>Publisher:</strong><br/>
          Yanis Amani<br/>
          Computer Science Student at HE-Arc Neuchâtel<br/>
          Espace de l'Europe 11, 2000 Neuchâtel, Switzerland<br/>
          Email: <a href="mailto:yanis.amani@icloud.com" class="text-orange-400 hover:underline">yanis.amani@icloud.com</a></p>

          <p class="mt-6 mb-2"><strong>Hosting Provider:</strong><br/>
          Netlify, Inc.<br/>
          44 Montgomery Street, Suite 300<br/>
          San Francisco, California 94104<br/>
          USA<br/>
          Website: <a href="https://www.netlify.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-orange-400 hover:underline">netlify.com</a></p>
        </div>

        <!-- Privacy Policy -->
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-4">2. Privacy Policy (GDPR Compliance)</h2>
          
          <h3 class="text-white font-semibold mb-2 mt-6">Data Collection & Processing</h3>
          <p class="mb-4">This website is built with a privacy-first approach. It does <strong>not</strong> use any tracking cookies, analytics scripts (like Google Analytics), or third-party marketing trackers. Your visit is strictly private.</p>
          <p class="mb-4">When you visit this website, the hosting provider (Netlify) automatically collects standard server logs necessary for the technical operation and security of the site. This may temporarily include your IP address, browser type, operating system, and the time of your request. This data is not used to identify you personally.</p>

          <h3 class="text-white font-semibold mb-2 mt-6">Contacting Me</h3>
          <p class="mb-4">If you reach out via the provided email address, your email and any personal data included within your message will be stored solely for the purpose of communicating with you and handling your inquiry. This data will never be shared with third parties without your explicit consent.</p>

          <h3 class="text-white font-semibold mb-2 mt-6">Your Rights</h3>
          <p class="mb-4">Under the General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR) and the Swiss Federal Act on Data Protection (FADP), you have the right to request access to, rectification of, or deletion of any personal data I may hold about you. Since this website does not collect personal data directly, this primarily applies to any email correspondence.</p>
          <p>To exercise these rights, please contact me at: <a href="mailto:yanis.amani@icloud.com" class="text-orange-400 hover:underline">yanis.amani@icloud.com</a>.</p>

          <h3 class="text-white font-semibold mb-2 mt-6">External Links</h3>
          <p class="mb-4">This portfolio contains links to external websites (such as GitHub or LinkedIn). I am not responsible for the privacy practices or content of these third-party platforms.</p>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
